    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains composed with recent bushing refreshes and documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, with the double VANOS system serviced and rod bearings addressed. A purist\u2019s spec for those who value tactile feedback and high-revving atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
