    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a beautifully maintained Obsidian Black sedan that perfectly captures the essence of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, barely noticeable door ding on the passenger side\u2014typical signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of premium Tan leather; the seats are plush and supportive, with only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and the premium surround-sound system, is in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs flawlessly, backed by a comprehensive service history. We recently completed a full synthetic oil change and installed a new set of Michelin all-season tires. The car handles beautifully with no rattles or vibrations, providing a smooth and confident ride. This is a solid, reliable luxury vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
