      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been absolutely wonderful to me. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years\u2014runs like a dream and is perfect for anyone looking for a dependable daily driver. There\u2019s a little bit of normal wear and tear, but honestly, it still looks great and feels even better on the road! I\u2019ve kept up with the maintenance, so it's ready to hit the pavement with a new owner. Send me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
